videos.headline: Howell finds a crossing Walston for the 11-yard TD
videos.description: Sam Howell finds a wide-open Garrett Walston, who dives into the end zone for North Carolina's first touchdown of the season.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell finds a crossing Walston for the 11-yard TD) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Syracuse's Jones picks off Howell
videos.description: Syracuse defensive back Mikel Jones hauls in the tipped pass for the interception.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Syracuse's Jones picks off Howell) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Syracuse recovers a muffed punt
videos.description: North Carolina's Dazz Newsome drops the punt and it's recovered by Nolan Cooney for Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Syracuse recovers a muffed punt) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Howell throws 2nd INT of the day
videos.description: North Carolina's Sam Howell tries to go deep but he's intercepted by Syracuse's Andre Cisco who returns it to midfield.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Howell throws 2nd INT of the day) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams powers way into end zone for the UNC TD
videos.description: Javonte Williams follows his offensive line and finds the end zone for the 1-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Williams powers way into end zone for the UNC TD) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter's impressive catch and run sets up UNC TD
videos.description: Michael Carter shows off his agility with an impressive 23-yard catch. On the next play, Javonte Williams scores the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Carter's impressive catch and run sets up UNC TD) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown, Williams team up for impressive UNC TD drive
videos.description: Dyami Brown hauls in the pass and powers his way to the Syracuse 6. Then on the next play, Javonte Williams scores his 3rd touchdown of the day.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown, Williams team up for impressive UNC TD drive) 2020/09/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams' three 2nd-half TDs lead UNC to win
videos.description: North Carolina running back Javonte Williams finds the end zone three times in the second half leading them to a dominant win over Syracuse.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Williams’ three 2nd-half TDs lead UNC to win) 2020/09/12 ESHEET SOTFULL
